---
source: crates/dreamd-cli/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "subcommand_help(\"mcp\")"
---
Start the MCP server (bridges to daemon if running, otherwise in-process)

Usage: mcp [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --manual-only
          Hard-lock dream cycle to manual-only mode (overrides config.toml)

      --project-root <PATH>
          Override the project root used for agent-root discovery. Required when the IDE launches the MCP server from a non-project CWD (e.g. Cursor's global ~/.cursor/mcp.json). Must be an absolute path to the directory that contains `.agent/`

  -h, --help
          Print help
